				<li id="16565513" class="cmnt-root" data="10" data-d="1648035471000"><ul class="comments"><li class="comment-box"><div class="avatar"><img src="/images/avatar.png" alt="" /><a class="comment-username" href="https://fextralife.com/forums/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&u=136081" rel="nofollow"  target="_blank" style="color: #;">luigislam</a></div><div class="comment"><div class="title"><span class="txt-subject"></span><input style="display: none;" class="txt-subject-ed"><span class="right cmt-ui"><a href="https://fextralife.com/forums/t578097/Ghiza's-Wheel" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">23 Mar 2022 07:37</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;<a class="report-post" href="https://fextralife.com/forums/report.php?f=193&p=16565513" rel="nofollow" target="_blank" title="report this post"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-flag" aria-hidden="true"></span></a></span></div><p class="txt-comment">Shielded enemies ai struggle to deal with 1H R2 because they might try to guard counter on the initial slam and then eat grind because they let their guard down. If they don&apos;t guard counter then they&apos;ll be locked into blocking the attack and usually most enemies with a shield can&apos;t block it fully or will be guard broken with the next attack. It has enough range for followup R1 or R2 to catch most basic enemies back dodge or side dodge or at least the small aoe knockback effect will catch them and cause brief stagger allowing you to not get punished. 1H R2 is than the Ash of War for dmg, bleed buildup, poise, and poise dmg but it only suffers when trying to hit in uneven terrain or bad hitboxes. Mimic tear is too inconsistent to use this weapon effectively the way we do and the weapon skill has like no poise so... yeah. Horrible for PvP but decently good for PvE. Its not going to Bleed like top bleed builds but it does it at a decent enough pace to feel &quot;balanced&quot; that I don&apos;t feel cheap for using it. Bleed still op though as of the time of this posting. </p><textarea style="display: none;" class="txt-comment-ed"></textarea><div class="clearfix"><a role="button" data-toggle="collapse" href="#zz-16565513" class="cmt-reply pull-right" href=""><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-share-alt"></span>Reply</a><a id="btnExpandComment" role="button" data-toggle="collapse" href="#replies-16565513" class="cmt-reply pull-right" href=""><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-share-alt"></span>Replies (<span class="replies">0</span>)</a><div class="vote pull-right"><section class="t-up"><span></span><p>12</p><i class="add">+1</i></section><section class="t-down"><span></span><p>2</p><i class="sub">-1</i></section></div></div><div class="collapse-com transparent"><div class="col-trigger collapse" id="zz-16565513"><div class="ng-scope"><textarea id="dcomment" class="ng-pristine ng-untouched ng-invalid ng-invalid-required" placeholder="Input your comments:"></textarea><button id="btn-16565513" class="btn btn-default btnPostReply"><i class="glyphicon glyphicon-pencil"></i> Submit</button><img id="newCommentAvatar" src="/images/avatar.png"/></div></div></div></div><div class="clearfix"></div><ul class="children collapse" id="replies-16565513"></ul></li></ul></li>
			
